ComicInfo.Summary:
Supreme and the Funny Book Felonies!: Fake Supreme newspaper sequence as if from the 1950s, where Supreme encounters fictional characters from the newspaper comic strips.
The Secret Origin of the Professor Night/Supreme Team!: How Supreme and Professor Night first met as teenagers.
National Flashlight Battery Inspection Day!: 1960s style public service announcement to precede the 1960s style story that follows.
The Return Of Darius Dax! Part 2: Darius Dax is defeated and there's a surprise revelation as to his eventual fate.
